\sphinxAtStartPar
These are some notes on the first week of courses held from 27 September through 1 October 2021 via Zoom.
The first five modules (Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday) have been tought by \sphinxhref{https://www.vlerick.com/en/find-faculty-and-experts/katleen-de-stobbeleir/}{Katleen De Stobbeleir}.

\sphinxAtStartPar
The ‘literature search \& review’ topic (Thursday, Friday) was covered by \sphinxhref{https://www.vlerick.com/en/find-faculty-and-experts/veroniek-collewaert/}{Veroniek Collewaert}.
